name: The golden old times
description:
I travel a lot. A lot. I also had to learn every day.

Travel for me was a personal challenge. The first step makes me feel insecure and so anxious. I was afraid and suffering fear about my future. My stomach was hurting initially, and my mind was unsafe until km started to come to me.

The first place I arrived after exit my country was San Pedro de Atacama. I went up by bike on this road. Tired, I stopped to drink some water and breath, in that moment I turned back and just realized where I was. 

I was huge.

That day I felt how much lucky I was to be there. How lucky I was for the energy that was crossing me.

I learned that I don´t need so much security to travel cause it will never be enough.
I just needed to jump and find myself into the adventure.

That day my body, my soul, my mind were in the same place. I was no longer suffering anymore.
